Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:22.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}福地洞天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:26.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}世界從來都是如此
